Motion2D 1.3.8 is an open source release.


This file describes the changes between Motion2D 1.3.7 and 1.3.8.

****************************************************************************
*                           General                                        *
****************************************************************************

- Possibility to get the covariance matrix of the estimated motion model
  parameters.
- Bug fixes.

****************************************************************************
*                           Library                                        *
****************************************************************************

- In CMotion2DEstimator, addition of new methods to get the covariance 
  matrix of the estimated motion model parameters: 
   . CMotion2DEstimator::computeCovarianceMatrix()
   . CMotion2DEstimator::isCovarianceMatrixComputed()
   . CMotion2DEstimator::getCovarianceMatrix(). 

- In CMotion2DEstimator, the method CMotion2DEstimator::initialize() was
  removed (it becomes obsolete).

- In CMotion2DPyramid, suppression of memory leeks when images are very
  small.


****************************************************************************
*                           Examples                                        *
****************************************************************************

- The Motion2D example:
   . addition of an option (-z) to compute and print the covariance matrix of
     the estimated motion model parameters.


****************************************************************************
*                           Documentation                                  *
****************************************************************************

- Some improvements.
